## Workflow

1. **EDA** — Understand the data (`notebooks/01_eda.ipynb`)
2. **Features** — Build feature pipeline (`src/features.py`)
3. **Baseline** — Quick model to set floor (`notebooks/02_baseline.ipynb`)
4. **Iterate** — Experiment, tune, ensemble
5. **Submit** — Generate & version submissions (`src/submit.py`)

## Notes

- Keep raw data immutable — never edit files in `data/raw/`
- Use `comp-starter submit --file <path>` to version submissions
- Track experiment ideas in this README or a separate doc
